  "name": "showcase-cove",
  "description": "Capability showcase two — dusk shoreline camp. Every 2026-07 feature is load-bearing: a lofted fishing boat (type: loft, curvature edge wear, mirrored oars), palm trunks and a stovepipe shaped by deformers, a boardwalk and lantern line arrayed along curved paths with per-instance jitter, cargo grids jittered out of clone reads, posed workers (sitting / waving) from one articulated module, a CSG hut with triplanar-detail walls, and everything snapToGround-ed onto a heightfield cove with seeded, snapped scatter. Probe-clean by construction.",
